&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2022. 9. 19. 15:32&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="1430" height="1578" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/224ccba6-ce2e-4487-8984-c3350e339fe5" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;속이답답한것인지 걍날씨가좋아서인지 자꾸 집에못있겠어서 놀이터가서 노래틀어놓고 하염없이 앉아있음&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="828" height="1792" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/18a0e5e6-e24f-4fdd-8d2e-bef57c7412e0" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ㅋㅋㅋ 사회에 던져졌는데 생각보다 내가 처신너무못해서 이런거 찾아보고있음&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="828" height="1792" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/07604dd0-487f-4687-b3be-0e4f26a3dc04" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;새로산 모자 ~~
맘에 든당&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/9140945b-57b7-4a54-8da6-b5bf5eaa1213" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;예뻐보여서 찍었음
늦여름감성 🌊🌊&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a20a524c-8d76-451a-81f0-0a274bc1644f" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;이렇게 입을까 했는데 뒷모습이너무 안예쁜것같기도해서 폐기함&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/b27c6f55-c0b2-4d9b-beb1-e0061f7ae90e" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;오늘 뭔가 입을게 없어서 검정 입었는데 나쁘지않았네&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/a3fafbe1-87a3-4d88-aafa-f9f555cc7270" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/2d991d0f-6aa2-4272-b58d-0137e9d9f929" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;애매한 시간에 나오니 한적하고 좋았다 !!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>그런날</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2022/22blog20/</link><pubDate>Sat, 10 Sep 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2022/22blog20/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="그런날"&gt;
 그런날
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%ea%b7%b8%eb%9f%b0%eb%82%a0"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2022. 9. 10. 20:37&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;나는오늘하루 솔직하게 행동했고 그거면됐음&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://youtu.be/PgGy2dQO868"&gt;https://youtu.be/PgGy2dQO868&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;원래 그렇게 생각하지도않았던 부분들이 막 나올때가 있음. 그래서 오디오가비면 말을 그냥 안한다라고 38분에나온다 이사람 말은 왤케 위로가 되지 오늘여러모로 혼란속에좀있었는데 맘가라앉히고 투자해서 공부하려고간카페는 와이파이가 너무너무느려 30분동안헤매다 그냥나왔다. 이럴거면 운동이라도했으면 돈도아끼고 운동도됐겠지. 근데그냥왔다 그리고 마음을 다잡았다 이런일이생긴건 큰 재난이 일어나서가아니라 그냥 일어난거야 떨치고 다음삶을살면되는거야&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>난슬플때 일상을써</title><link>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2022/22blog19/</link><pubDate>Fri, 02 Sep 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://yshghid.github.io/docs/previous/2022/22blog19/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="난슬플때-일상을써"&gt;
 난슬플때 일상을써
 &lt;a class="anchor" href="#%eb%82%9c%ec%8a%ac%ed%94%8c%eb%95%8c-%ec%9d%bc%ec%83%81%ec%9d%84%ec%8d%a8"&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;#2022. 9. 2. 23:27&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="960" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ae6aeae3-5ab2-4509-b8c5-af0d749ccdc7" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;진짜너무맛있다 근데저 남산왕돈까스소스 다먹어서 이제없다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c68521ce-c4a4-4e8b-a58a-6fa22fddd3e3" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;살지말지 되게고민했는데 엄청잘입고다님&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0350035e-7c2d-4bb6-b960-0b6cf2015a7a" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;난지수가 내편지보고울었는지몰랐음 물론다른것을 보고 울었을수도있지만 난위로가됐다 그것만으로도&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/671cc3a2-cce2-46c2-b40b-2aba2aad610e" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;한창논문읽고있을때..
어휴
부담감왜그렇게심했지&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="796" height="1120" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1e594ab0-815f-46dd-914d-502569eb63bc" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;시간표 나는나름 괜찮음 아쉬운거하나도없고&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1705" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e5165d6d-07ae-45de-beca-9f5eb4bfef26" /&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1280" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0932c7ec-36ab-4ef1-8957-a84ba6d0ce5c" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;핏은 예쁜데 난해한 치마&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="1706" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/155e9f9b-eb51-418f-a28d-eaf32aa55428" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;머리짜르고 아점으로 먹었다
맛있었다&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img width="1280" height="960" alt="image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c02c5bc9-afc7-40ab-bbcf-1719fee7391a" /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;가을날씨된지얼마안된 시점에 마음이너무 안좋고 외로운마음이커서 벤치에누워서그냥 눈만뜨고있었다 하늘은너무이뻣다 노래는 투머치럽윌킬유 이런거 들었는데 무언가로부터 자유로워지고싶었던듯 감정이든 사람이든..
눈물은안났고 진짜그냥숨만쉬었다 사람들지나다니는거 보기싫어서 + 저녁되니까 정자에 불켜진게 눈부셔서 마스크 눈까지쓰고 누워있다가 답답해서뺐는데&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>